    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AbstractBook
    Abstract base class representing a generic Book.
    Book
    Represents a concrete implementation of a book, extending the AbstractBook class.
    Book.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating a new instance of Book.
    BookLibrary
    Represents a library system for managing books.
    Encyclopedia
    Represents an Encyclopedia, a specialized type of Book.
    Encyclopedia.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating an Encyclopedia.
    Librarian
    Represents a virtual assistant for interacting with the Book Library system.
    LibraryServices
    Represents a contract for a book library system.
    Main
    The entry point of the Book Library application.
    SpecialBook
    Represents a SpecialBook, a type of Book with additional unique properties.
    SpecialBook.Builder
    Builder pattern for creating a SpecialBook.
